thread.title: Senate Intelligence Committee Backs Conclusion That Moscow Attempted to Boost Trump

author: Byron Tau
title: Senate Intelligence Committee Backs Conclusion That Moscow Attempted to Boost Trump

organizations.name: senate intelligence committee backs conclusion that moscow attempted to boost trump

text:
WASHINGTON—A Republican-led Senate committee backed U.S. intelligence agencies’ finding that Moscow attempted to boost Donald Trump’s 2016 presidential campaign, breaking with a GOP-led House panel that examined the same material.
The conclusion on the January 2017 intelligence finding was part of the committee’s probe into Russian interference in the 2016 election, which continues.
